casebody.data:
Richard L. BASILI, Jr., Et Alia In Propria Persona
v.
Kimberly J. BASILI, Et Alia. No. 289P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 30, 2005. Richard L. Basili, Jr., Pro Se. W. Michael Spivey, Rocky Mount, for Kimberly J. Basili.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 31st day of May 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 30th day of June 2005."
